data.description: The renovated 3bed/2bath ranch home boasts a refreshed and modern aesthetic with numerous upgrades. The exterior has been enhanced with a newer roof, providing both durability and a polished look. As you approach the property, you'll notice the expansive over .80-acre lot, offering ample space for various outdoor activities.    Upon entering the home, the interior showcases a warm design. The flooring has been replaced with new, stylish materials, all new windows , blinds and exterior doors that bring in plenty of natural light, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere throughout the house.    The kitchen has been completely transformed with the addition of new appliances, bringing modern functionality and efficiency. Black appliances, sleek new countertops, back splash, and updated cabinetry all contribute to a chic and functional cooking space.    The master bathroom  features a spacious shower with stylish glass doors, complemented by new tiling and upgraded plumbing fixtures. The guest bathroom has also betransformed both rooms adding functionality to the space.    In addition to the mentioned renovations, the ranch home has undergone a transformative change by converting the garage into an oversized living room. This conversion not only increases the overall square footage but also adds a spacious and versatile living area to the home.    The oversized living room features a thoughtful design with built-in shelving, providing both functionality and aesthetics. The shelving units can serve various purposes, from displaying decorative items to accommodating books, electronics, or personal belongings. This built-in storage contributes to the organized and streamlined appearance of the living space.    With this garage conversion, the total square footage of the home now exceeds 1738 sq ft, offering ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. The oversized living room creates a central hub for relaxation and social activities, making it an ideal space for family gatherings, entertaining guests, or simply enjoying everyday life.    Moving outdoors, the fenced-in backyard provides a private and secure area for recreation and relaxation. The fencing ensures privacy and safety, making it an ideal space for pets or family gatherings. Additionally, two storage buildings have been added to the property 10x16 (less than 6mts old) and a 10x12 providing convenient space for storing tools, equipment, or other items.    The combination of the garage conversion, new roof, appliances, flooring, windows,bathroom renovations and the expansive lot with a fenced backyard and storage buildings results in a well-rounded and upgraded ranch home that seamlessly blends style, functionality, and ample living space.    Make your appointment to visit today.
